\v 3 Babadumela ngezandla\x + Luka 21.12.\x*, ba\add ba\add*faka esitokisini kwaze kwaba kusisa; ngoba kwasekuhlwile\x + 5.18.\x*.
\v 4 Kodwa abanengi abalizwayo ilizwi bakholwa; lenani lamadoda lalingaba zinkulungwane ezinhlanu\x + 2.41.\x*.
