\v 7 Sebebamise phakathi, babuza: Lokhu lina likwenze ngawaphi amandla kumbe ngaliphi ibizo\x + Mat. 21.23.\x*?
\v 8 Khona uPetro egcwaliswe nguMoya oNgcwele wathi kubo\x + 13.9. Mat. 10.20.\x*: Babusi babantu labadala bakoIsrayeli\x + 4.8,26. Joha. 3.1.\x*,
\v 9 nxa thina sibuzwa lamuhla ngomsebenzi omuhle emuntwini obuthakathaka emzimbeni\x + Luka 23.14. Seb. 12.19. 24.8. 28.18.\x*, \add ukuthi\add* yena usiliswe ngani\x + Mark. 10.52.\x*;
\v 10 kakwaziwe yini lonke laso sonke isizwe sakoIsrayeli, ukuthi ngebizo likaJesu Kristu umNazaretha\x + Joha. 20.31. Seb. 3.6, 16.\x*, lina elambethelayo, uNkulunkulu owamvusayo kwabafileyo\x + 2.24.\x*, ngaye lo umi lapha phambi kwenu esesilile.
\v 11 Yena lo uyilitshe\x + Hlab. 118.22. Mat. 21.42.\x* elaliwa yini abakhi, eseliyinhloko yengonsi\x + Mark. 9.12.\x*.
\v 12 Njalo kalukho usindiso komunye; ngoba kalikho lelinye ibizo ngaphansi kwezulu elinikiweyo phakathi kwabantu, esimele sisindiswe ngalo\x + 13.39. 1 Tim. 2.5. Mat. 1.21.\x*.
