\v 13 Kwathi bebona isibindi sikaPetro loJohane\x + 4.19. 1.13. 8.14.\x*, njalo besazi ukuthi\x + Mat. 11.25.\x* babengabantu abangafundanga njalo bengabantu nje\x + 1 Kor. 14.16,23,24. 2 Kor. 11.6.\x*, bamangala, njalo babazi ukuthi babeloJesu\x + Mat. 25.24.\x*,
