\v 15 Kodwa sebebalayile ukuthi baphume phandle emphakathini\x + Mat. 5.22.\x*, bacebisana bodwa,
\v 16 besithi: Sizabenzani lababantu\x + Joha. 11.47. 12.19.\x*? Ngoba ukuthi isibonakaliso esidumisekayo senziwa yibo, kusobala kubo bonke abahlezi eJerusalema, njalo singe\add ku\add*phike\x + 4.21. 3.9,10.\x*;
\v 17 kodwa ukuze kungabe kusanda phakathi kwabantu, asibaqonqosele ukuthi bangabe besakhuluma lamuntu ngalelibizo\x + Luka 22.15.\x*.
\v 18 Basebebabiza, babalaya ukuthi bangakhulumi lakanye njalo bangafundisi ngebizo likaJesu\x + 5.40. 5.28.\x*.
\v 19 Kodwa uPetro loJohane babaphendula bathi: Yehlukanisani ukuthi kulungile phambi kukaNkulunkulu ukulalela lina kuloNkulunkulu\x + 5.29.\x*.
\v 20 Ngoba thina\x + 1.8. 2.32. 4.33. Joha. 15.26.\x* kasilakuyekela ukukhuluma\x + 22.15. 1 Joha. 1.1,3.\x* izinto esizibonileyo lesizizwileyo.
\v 21 Kwathi sebe\add ba\add*qonqosele futhi, babayekela bahamba; bengatholi lutho lokuthi bangabajezisa njani, ngenxa yabantu\x + Mat. 21.26. Mark. 11.32. Luka 20.6,19. 22.2. Seb. 5.13,26.\x*, ngoba bonke badumisa uNkulunkulu\x + Mat. 15.31.\x* ngalokho okwenzakeleyo\x + 3.7,8.\x*.
\v 22 Ngoba umuntu wayeleminyaka edlula amatshumi amane esenziwa kuye lesisibonakaliso seselapho.
\s Ukukhuleka kwebandla
\p
\v 23 Kwathi sebeyekelwe basuka baya kwabakibo, bababikela konke abapristi abakhulu labadala abakutshiloyo kubo\x + 24.23. 1 Tim. 5.8. Joha. 1.11.\x*.
