\v 28 ukwenza konke isandla sakho lecebo lakho elakumisa phambili ukuthi kwenzeke\x + 2.23. 3.18. Luka 22.22.\x*.
\v 29 Njalo ngalesisikhathi, Nkosi, khangela ukusonga kwabo\x + 2 Kho. 19.16. Isa. 37.17.\x*, unike izinceku zakho ukuthi zikhulume ilizwi lakho ngesibindi sonke\x + 4.13,31. 9.27,29. 13.46. 14.3. 18.26. 19.8. 26.26. 28.31. Efe. 6.19. 1 Thes. 2.2.\x*,
\v 30 ngokuthi welule isandla sakho ukusilisa, lokuthi kwenziwe izibonakaliso lezimangaliso\x + Joha. 4.48.\x* ngebizo\x + 3.6.\x* leNdodana yakho engcwele uJesu\x + 4.27.\x*.
\v 31 Kwathi sebekhulekile kwazanyazanyiswa indawo ababebuthene kuyo\x + 16.26. 2.2.\x*, basebegcwaliswa bonke ngoMoya oNgcwele\x + 2.4.\x*, basebekhuluma ilizwi likaNkulunkulu ngesibindi\x + 4.13,31. 9.27,29. 13.46. 14.3. 18.26. 19.8. 26.26; 28.31. Efe. 6.19. 1 Thes. 2.2.\x*.
\s Ukuhlanganyela kwebandla izinto zonke
\p
\v 32 Lexuku labakholwayo lalinhliziyo\add nye\x + 2 Lan. 30.12.\x*\add* lomoya munye\x + Fil. 1.27.\x*; njalo kungekho oyedwa owathi ezintweni alazo ngezakhe, kodwa bahlanganyela izinto zonke\x + 2.44.\x*.
\v 33 Langamandla amakhulu\x + 1.8.\x* abaphostoli baveza ubufakazi\x + 1.22.\x* bokuvuka kweNkosi uJesu\x + 2.24.\x*, lomusa omkhulu waba phezu kwabo bonke\x + 2.47. Luka 2.40.\x*.
\v 34 Ngoba kwakungekho futhi oswelayo phakathi kwabo; ngoba bonke ababengabanikazi bemihlaba kumbe izindlu, bathengisa baletha intengo zalokho okuthengisiweyo\x + 2.45.\x*,
\v 35 ba\add yi\add*beka enyaweni zabaphostoli\x + 4.37. 5.2.\x*; njalo kwabelwa ngulowo lalowo\x + 6.1.\x* njengokuswela kwakhe\x + 2.45.\x*.
\v 36 Kwathi uJose owabizwa ngabaphostoli ngokuthi nguBarnabasi\x + 9.27. 11.22,25,30. 12.25. 13.15. 1 Kor. 9.6. Gal. 2.1,9,13. Kol. 4.10.\x*, okuyikuthi ngokuphendulelwa, indodana yenduduzo, umLevi, umKuprosi ngokuzalwa\x + 11.19,20. 13.4. 15.39. 21.3,16. 27.4.\x*,
